{"tid":1513753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前線急救要物資","createTime":"2019-08-28T12:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T14:49:13.000Z","uid":107498,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"de6a7d344796f33d25064c992d56c40d79606086","tid":1513753,"uid":107498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:55:08.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我地係一班前線first aider 亦都係一班學生<br />\n我地由6.12 打到 8.25 嚟緊到8.31 <br />\n我地由本身有物資 到有隊友俾狗捉左 過百支細生理鹽水同少量濾毒罐俾人充公<br />\n我地都咬實牙關撐落去 但係我地開始有隊友連飯都唔食 用哂d錢去買物資<br />\n所以想問下有無手足可以贊助d物資俾我地 等我地可以撐落去<br />\n徵求物資:<br />\n1. 3M 濾毒罐 P100 <br />\n2. 3M 3200 濾毒罐 3301K-100<br />\n3. 3M 過濾棉<br />\n4. 生理鹽水(細支)<br />\n<strong>不收現金 只收物資</strong><br />\n有經濟能力嘅希望可以幫下我地 未有能力嘅留言講句加油 or 推下post就OK <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"faf55edd22123a0b5b8b2cedeb1b422e9f1aa8ae","tid":1513753,"uid":270828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:58:17.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"64a4c1f4ba3c45d5c23825de43e552fd13a455a3","tid":1513753,"uid":166452,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T12:58:52.000Z","msg":"點俾你地？我其實隨身帶住 但每次經過交俾你地first aid 你地都唔收⋯"},{"pid":"6823337af306f490c31b177ec0922a7af79fff3e","tid":1513753,"uid":313555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:00:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83423e5fdac841b16b00c7b6fc85db89db7c9023","tid":1513753,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0jwbU4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0jwbU4.png&h=75debaf3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fQo8Yz5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfQo8Yz5.jpg&h=d0737e43&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/28/210051_a79fba2dfc25e811a925b932ce886423.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eser